2369
00:46:13,273 --> 00:46:15,023
Geto Suguru.

2370
00:46:16,523 --> 00:46:19,033
He's one of the four special-grade sorcerers.

2371
00:46:19,573 --> 00:46:26,033
The one who was banished from Jujutsu Tech 
for cursing over a hundred normal people to death.

2372
00:46:26,033 --> 00:46:28,583
The worst curse user around. {not _ever_ since that would be kamo noritoshi}

