00:54:16,673 --> 00:54:17,753
I'm sorry.

2778
00:54:18,843 --> 00:54:21,603
I don't really understand what you're talking about.

2779
00:54:22,733 --> 00:54:23,803
But...

2780
00:54:24,933 --> 00:54:28,563
I'm not going to help 
someone who talks down to my friends!

2781
00:54:30,933 --> 00:54:34,433
My apologies. It wasn't my intention to upset you.

2782
00:54:34,433 --> 00:54:37,903
Then what exactly did you come here for?

2783
00:54:39,433 --> 00:54:41,743
To declare war.

2784
00:54:42,423 --> 00:54:48,243
To all those gathered here,
 clear out your ears and listen up very closely.

2785
00:54:48,873 --> 00:54:55,463
On the coming December 24th, at sundown, 
we will commence the Night Parade of a Hundred Demons!

2786
00:54:56,003 --> 00:55:00,763
It will take place in the Crucible of Curses,
 Tokyo's Shinjuku Ward.

2787
00:54:59,843 --> 00:55:00,763
Kabuki Town, First Street

